The article is about the passing of Sheldon Adelson, and the condolences expressed by Melania and Donald Trump. Adelson is described as someone who lived the American dream, with his ingenuity and creativity earning him immense wealth. He is also praised for his character, philanthropy, and support of Israel. Adelson advocated for the relocation of the US embassy to Jerusalem, recognition of Israeli sovereignty over the Golan Heights, and peace between Israel and its neighbors. The article concludes by stating that Adelson will be greatly missed and that the world has lost a great man.